- But violent how? Did he do something to you?
- No, no, no. He didn't do anything to me.

15
00:00:50,800 --> 00:00:53,580
But he went mad. Plus, he thinks I'm seeing someone else.

16
00:00:53,640 --> 00:00:56,200
Obviously, he thinks I'm seeing a guy.

17
