Share the things I like with the people that I love, so...

40
00:02:23,460 --> 00:02:27,180
Well, when I start working again, I'll pay you back every cent, okay?

41
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:28,580
Mom.

42
00:02:29,060 --> 00:02:31,660
You haven't even fully recovered and you're already thinking about working?

43
00:02:31,660 --> 00:02:33,820
Honey, we need the money.

44
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:38,020
- If we need money, I'll work. Not you.
- No.

45
00:02:38,580 --> 00:02:39,480
Look.

46
00:02:40,240 --> 00:02:43,520
We already talked about it. I want you to go back to school.

47
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:48,020
