48
00:02:49,980 --> 00:02:53,920
I missed the admission exam. It happened when we were at the hospital.

49
00:02:57,060 --> 00:02:58,140
I'm sorry.

50
00:02:59,140 --> 00:03:01,280
I know you really wanted to do that.

51
00:03:01,600 --> 00:03:04,420
- We'll look for a way to fix it, okay?
- Okay.

52
00:03:05,900 --> 00:03:09,520
I'm very sorry you missed it because you were taking care of me.

53
00:03:10,060 --> 00:03:11,420
Mom, it's fine.

54
00:03:11,580 --> 00:03:13,080
We can still fix it, right?

55
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,780
Yes, for sure.

56
00:03:14,920 --> 00:00:00,000
Well, the moment I'm recovered, we'll leave this town and I'll work very hard so you can go back to school.

